Item.Review:
Pros: BASS, Color, Acessories
Cons: Batteries, Spendy
These look amazing, Look like candy! Their sound is good, Bass is great. Feel pretty sturdy unlike old solos. Recomend to hip-hop lovers. Great to make an impression as a DJ. Although i wouldnt use them for Djing because the seem sturdy for a normal listener but not a DJ that would keep moving them and rolling them cause then we might run into some durability issues. Over all they are a good purchace if you like rap and similar stuff. My favorite songs to play on them... Drop it Low In da Club Boom Boom Pow Any Dr. Dre (;
